{"article_id":"GK0Pzms7ZZeSsJTy","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Former Vice President Joe Biden talks to journalists during a campaign event in Mt . Pleasant , Iowa , January 31 , 2020 .","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"( Carlos Barria/Reuters )","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"In an interview , Joe Biden ' s accuser expressed outrage","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"that Democratic politicians had not given her Biden allegations a fair hearing .","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"NRPLUS MEMBER ARTICLE","depth":2},{"id":5,"text":"A s someone","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"who spent her career","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"working for Democratic politicians","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"and advocating liberal causes ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Tara Reade was shocked by the treatment","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"she ' s received from her co-partisans","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"since publicly accusing Joe Biden of sexually assaulting her","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"when she worked as a staff assistant in his office in 1993 .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"Reade , 56 , claims","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"that in the spring or summer of 1993 , a senior staffer told her to meet Biden in a Capitol corridor","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"to deliver a duffel bag .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"While there ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"she says ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Biden forced her against the wall","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"and penetrated her with his fingers .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"She first made the allegation during a podcast with political reporter Katie Halper last month","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"and has since described the alleged ordeal in interviews with the New York Times , the Washington Post , and Business Insider .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"Reade told in a Tuesday phone interview","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"that ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"since coming forward ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"she ' s been subjected to \" shocking \" treatment from those","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"she had expected to come to her aid :","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"the very people","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"who championed a woman ' s \" right \"","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"to be believed during the Kavanaugh confirmation episode two years prior ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"which","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"Reade confirmed","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"she followed at the time .","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"Biden ' s guilt has by no means been established .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"But the candidate himself has yet to be asked about the allegation at all","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"-","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"despite sitting for interviews with a host of prominent reporters over the past month .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"His campaign spokeswoman has re-upped a single categorical denial","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"when asked for comment","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"following each new development .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"Two women ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"one a former neighbor and the other a former coworker , recently told Business Insider","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"that Reade described the incident in separate conversations","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"two years after it allegedly occurred .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"Reade ' s brother and one friend have also said","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"she told them about the assault","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"soon after it happened .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"But other former Biden staffers ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"including several","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"that Reade says","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"she had told about the incident ,","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"have denied her account .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Reade initially claimed in 2019","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"that Biden had touched her back and neck in a way","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"that made her feel uncomfortable ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"but she didn ' t say anything about sexual assault .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"She now attributes that apparent inconsistency to fear about the repercussions","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"of making such an extreme claim about a presidential nominee .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"\" I was too frightened","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"to come forward at first , \"","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"Reade said ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"that she nearly overcame her initial trepidation in the fall ,","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"but stopped short of publicizing the allegation","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"after receiving a death threat .","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"Reade emphasized","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"when she came forward with her allegation ,","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"she didn ' t expect the reaction","depth":15},{"id":69,"text":"that Democrats , journalists , and Me Too activists displayed during the Kavanaugh confirmation -","depth":15},{"id":70,"text":"just the minimal level of respect","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"accorded to women","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"alleging sexual assault in more \" normal \" circumstances .","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"( Kavanaugh accuser Christine Blasey Ford was unable to present a single contemporaneous witness","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"to support her account . )","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"\" I was just hoping to get a fair and equal treatment , \"","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"Reade says ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"\" but","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"because it ' s Joe Biden","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"I ' ve been silenced or smeared . \"","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"Immediately after her appearance on Halper ' s podcast ,","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"Reade claims ,","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"the Biden campaign dug through her private Instagram account","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"and scoured her years-old online writing ,","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"in which she praises Russia and Vladimir Putin ,","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"and sent the results to the New York Times","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"in order to cast doubt on her allegation .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"She also alleges","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"that the campaign used bots","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"to spread the narrative","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"that she was a Russian agent .","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"was unable to confirm either accusation .","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"Much of the ensuing coverage by left-leaning and mainstream publications","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"- the same outlets","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"that credulously accepted Ford ' s allegation as fact -","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"has included descriptions of Reade ' s past Putin flattery","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"and emphasized her support for Bernie Sanders ' s primary candidacy ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"raising the possibility","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"that Reade had ulterior motives","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"in escalating her allegations against Biden","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"to include sexual assault .","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"While the Biden campaign ' s hostile response to the allegation constituted an understandable damage-control effort from a man on the cusp of the presidency ,","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"Reade thought","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"she might at least get a hearing from prominent female Democrats","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"who have championed sexual-assault survivors in the past .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"Before she went public with the allegation ,","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"in an effort","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"to secure a platform","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"to tell her story ,","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"Reade sent letters to senators Elizabeth Warren","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"( Mass . )","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"and Kamala Harris","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"( Calif. )","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"in the fall of last year ,","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"laying out the allegation","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"and asking for help","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"in publicizing Biden ' s conduct .","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"Warren ,","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"who argued on the floor of the Senate","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"that Blasey Ford ' s allegation was sufficient","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"to disqualify Brett Kavanaugh ,","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"responded with a form letter","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"informing Reade","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"that she couldn ' t help","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"because Reade was not a constituent of hers","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"and suggesting","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"that she reach out to her own representatives .","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"Harris ,","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"who similarly insisted on the veracity of Blasey Ford ' s claim","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"despite the lack of evidence ,","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"didn ' t respond to Reade ' s letter at all .","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"\" Why would you not call me","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"or reach out to me directly ?","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"What do you really believe regarding harassment","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"because you say","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"we should stick up for vulnerable people .","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"I was vulnerable ,","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"I was just a staff assistant , \"","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"Reade said","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"when asked what message","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"she would like to convey to Harris and Warren .","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"\" Are they going to allow me to continue being smeared","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"or are they going to stand up for me ? \"","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"Since going public on Halper ' s podcast ,","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"Reade has reached out to the offices of senator Bernie Sanders","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"( I. , Vt. )","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"and representative Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"( D. , N.Y. ) .","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"She said","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"she was particularly disappointed with Ocasio-Cortez ,","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"given the freshman congresswoman ' s past comments about gender disparity in the workplace and the importance","depth":14},{"id":151,"text":"of amplifying the voices of sexual-assault survivors .","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"\" I watched AOC give a speech","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"about protecting people","depth":14},{"id":154,"text":"being taken advantage of in the workplace , \"","depth":14},{"id":155,"text":"Reade said .","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"\" Where does she stand now ?","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"She endorsed Joe Biden .","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"Why are you endorsing my rapist ? \"","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"Ocasio-Cortez , Warren , and Harris all failed to respond to a request for comment by press time .","depth":8},{"id":160,"text":"Their fellow Democrats have been similarly mute","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"- save for Senator Kirsten Gillibrand of New York ,","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"who once urged an FBI investigation into Kavanaugh ' s conduct .","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"She said","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"she \" stands by \" Biden","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"when asked Tuesday about Reade ' s claim .","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"\" He ' s devoted his life to supporting women ,","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"and he has vehemently denied this allegation , \"","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"she told reporters on a conference call .","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"Reade","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"-","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"who ,","depth":14},{"id":172,"text":"in addition to working for Biden , worked for Representative Leon Panetta and California state senator Jack O ' Connell , both Democrats -","depth":14},{"id":173,"text":"says","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"she has left the Democratic Party for good","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"and will never vote for another Democrat at the national level .","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"\" I think","depth":13},{"id":177,"text":"the DNC is a sham","depth":13},{"id":178,"text":"and their silence around what happened to me as a Democratic staffer is unconscionable , \"","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"she said .","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"\" I was on the job","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"when I got raped .","depth":12},{"id":182,"text":"They are complicit in rape . \"","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":365,"left":186,"right":364,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":186,"left":184,"right":185,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":184,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":364,"left":4,"right":363,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":363,"left":213,"right":362,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":213,"left":200,"right":212,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":193,"right":199,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":193,"left":189,"right":192,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":189,"left":5,"right":188,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":6,"right":187,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":192,"left":190,"right":191,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":190,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":195,"right":198,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,